The only known certainty is that every summer the Vans Warped Tour will roll into town with 50-plus alternative, pop-punk, metalcore and ska bands to mark the beginning of summer. This year, Dallas is the official first stop of the 41-city tour, almost guaranteeing local fans will see their new favorite bands at their most energetic and anxious to deliver their best show possible before the heat and strain of travel bogs them down.
